      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi026.m4a",
      "text": "それは嫌だよ。一度引き受けた仕事を断るなんて\n先方に迷惑が掛かるじゃないか",
